Final Keyword
==============
-> Final is a reserved keyword in java.
->Final class can not be inherited.
->Final variable are nothing but constants.Final variable value cannot be modified.
            Ex: public final int id =101;
                 id = 104;//invalid

->Final method can not overriden.We can't override final methods .
->We can use this keyword at three place.
          
          1.Class level
          2.Variable level
          3.Method level

